PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>

SELECT ( ?property AS ?property__out )
( COUNT(?person) AS ?person__out )
( SAMPLE(?propertyLabel) AS ?propertyLabel__out )

WHERE {

      
      VALUES ?tmp0 { <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q15632617> }. 
 ?person <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/P31>/<http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/P279>* ?tmp0. 
 ?person ?property ?any1 . 
 
?any2 <http://wikiba.se/ontology#directClaim> ?property .
      FILTER (BOUND(?property))
      
      
  
      
      
      OPTIONAL { { ?propertyClaim <http://wikiba.se/ontology#directClaim> ?property .
?propertyClaim rdfs:label ?propertyLabel . } 
UNION
 { ?property rdfs:label ?propertyLabel . }
FILTER (BOUND(?propertyLabel) && lang(?propertyLabel) = "en"). }
    
}
GROUP BY
    (?property)
HAVING ( ( COUNT(?person) ) >= 1 )
ORDER BY desc(( COUNT(?person) ))
LIMIT 20

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>

SELECT ( ?timeResult AS ?time__out )
( COUNT(?person) AS ?person__out )
( ?gender AS ?gender__out )
( SAMPLE(?timeLabel) AS ?timeLabel__out )
( SAMPLE(?genderLabel) AS ?genderLabel__out )

WHERE {

      
      VALUES ?tmp0 { <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/P166> }. 
 ?person ?tmp0 ?award . 
 VALUES ?tmp1 { <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/P166>
<http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/P166>
<http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/P166> }. 
 ?award ?tmp1 ?awardValue . 
 ?tmp2 <http://wikiba.se/ontology#claim> ?tmp0 . 
 VALUES ?tmp3 { <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/P585>
<http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/P585>
<http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/P585> }. 
 ?award ?tmp3 ?time . 
 VALUES ?tmp4 { <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q5> }. 
 ?person <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/P31>/<http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/P279>* ?tmp4. 
 VALUES ?tmp5 { <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q7191> }. 
 ?awardValue <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/P279>+ ?tmp5. 
 VALUES ?tmp6 { <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/P21> }. 
 ?person ?tmp6 ?gender .
      
        FILTER(BOUND(?time) && DATATYPE(?time) IN (<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date>,<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>)).
        FILTER(YEAR(?time) > 0 && YEAR(?time) < 2100).
      
      FILTER (BOUND(?gender))
      
  
      { SELECT (MIN((YEAR(?time) + MONTH(?time) / 12)) AS ?timeMin)
(MAX((YEAR(?time) + MONTH(?time) / 12)) AS ?timeMax) WHERE { 
      VALUES ?tmp0 { <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/P166> }. 
 ?person ?tmp0 ?award . 
 VALUES ?tmp1 { <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/P166>
<http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/P166>
<http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/P166> }. 
 ?award ?tmp1 ?awardValue . 
 ?tmp2 <http://wikiba.se/ontology#claim> ?tmp0 . 
 VALUES ?tmp3 { <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/P585>
<http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/P585>
<http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/P585> }. 
 ?award ?tmp3 ?time . 
 VALUES ?tmp4 { <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q5> }. 
 ?person <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/P31>/<http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/P279>* ?tmp4. 
 VALUES ?tmp5 { <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q7191> }. 
 ?awardValue <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/P279>+ ?tmp5. 
 VALUES ?tmp6 { <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/P21> }. 
 ?person ?tmp6 ?gender .
      
        FILTER(BOUND(?time) && DATATYPE(?time) IN (<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date>,<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>)).
        FILTER(YEAR(?time) > 0 && YEAR(?time) < 2100).
      
      FILTER (BOUND(?gender))
      
   } }
BIND( ((?timeMax - ?timeMin) / 20) AS ?timeStep )
BIND( (YEAR(?time) + MONTH(?time) / 12) AS ?timeContinue )
BIND( (0.5 + xsd:integer((?timeContinue - ?timeMin) / ?timeStep)) * ?timeStep + ?timeMin AS ?timeDiscrete )
BIND( ?timeDiscrete AS ?timeResult )
      
      OPTIONAL { { ?timeClaim <http://wikiba.se/ontology#directClaim> ?time .
?timeClaim rdfs:label ?timeLabel . } 
UNION
 { ?time rdfs:label ?timeLabel . }
FILTER (BOUND(?timeLabel) && lang(?timeLabel) = "en"). }
OPTIONAL { { ?genderClaim <http://wikiba.se/ontology#directClaim> ?gender .
?genderClaim rdfs:label ?genderLabel . } 
UNION
 { ?gender rdfs:label ?genderLabel . }
FILTER (BOUND(?genderLabel) && lang(?genderLabel) = "en"). }
    
}
GROUP BY
    (?timeResult)
    (?gender)
HAVING ( ( COUNT(?person) ) >= 1 )
ORDER BY desc(( COUNT(?person) ))
LIMIT 400

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>

SELECT ( ?dobResult AS ?dob__out )
( COUNT(?main) AS ?main__out )
( ?gender AS ?gender__out )
( SAMPLE(?dobLabel) AS ?dobLabel__out )
( SAMPLE(?genderLabel) AS ?genderLabel__out )

WHERE {

      
      VALUES ?tmp0 { <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/P21> }. 
 ?main ?tmp0 ?gender . 
 VALUES ?tmp1 { <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/P106> }. 
 VALUES ?tmp2 { <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q169470> }. 
 ?main ?tmp1 ?tmp2 . 
 VALUES ?tmp3 { <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/P569> }. 
 ?main ?tmp3 ?dob .
      
        FILTER(BOUND(?dob) && DATATYPE(?dob) IN (<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date>,<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>)).
        FILTER(YEAR(?dob) > 0 && YEAR(?dob) < 2100).
      
      FILTER (BOUND(?gender))
      
  
      { SELECT (MIN((YEAR(?dob) + MONTH(?dob) / 12)) AS ?dobMin)
(MAX((YEAR(?dob) + MONTH(?dob) / 12)) AS ?dobMax) WHERE { 
      VALUES ?tmp0 { <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/P21> }. 
 ?main ?tmp0 ?gender . 
 VALUES ?tmp1 { <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/P106> }. 
 VALUES ?tmp2 { <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q169470> }. 
 ?main ?tmp1 ?tmp2 . 
 VALUES ?tmp3 { <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/P569> }. 
 ?main ?tmp3 ?dob .
      
        FILTER(BOUND(?dob) && DATATYPE(?dob) IN (<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date>,<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>)).
        FILTER(YEAR(?dob) > 0 && YEAR(?dob) < 2100).
      
      FILTER (BOUND(?gender))
      
   } }
BIND( ((?dobMax - ?dobMin) / 41) AS ?dobStep )
BIND( (YEAR(?dob) + MONTH(?dob) / 12) AS ?dobContinue )
BIND( (0.5 + xsd:integer((?dobContinue - ?dobMin) / ?dobStep)) * ?dobStep + ?dobMin AS ?dobDiscrete )
BIND( ?dobDiscrete AS ?dobResult )
      
      OPTIONAL { { ?dobClaim <http://wikiba.se/ontology#directClaim> ?dob .
?dobClaim rdfs:label ?dobLabel . } 
UNION
 { ?dob rdfs:label ?dobLabel . }
FILTER (BOUND(?dobLabel) && lang(?dobLabel) = "en"). }
OPTIONAL { { ?genderClaim <http://wikiba.se/ontology#directClaim> ?gender .
?genderClaim rdfs:label ?genderLabel . } 
UNION
 { ?gender rdfs:label ?genderLabel . }
FILTER (BOUND(?genderLabel) && lang(?genderLabel) = "en"). }
    
}
GROUP BY
    (?dobResult)
    (?gender)
HAVING ( ( COUNT(?main) ) >= 6 )
ORDER BY desc(( COUNT(?main) ))
LIMIT 820

PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>

SELECT ?type (COUNT(?s) as ?count)

WHERE {

      ?s rdf:type ?type .
    
}
GROUP BY
    (?type)

ORDER BY desc(?count)
LIMIT 200
